{"type":"excalidraw","version":2,"source":"mcp-excalidraw-server","elements":[{"id":"title","type":"text","x":150,"y":0,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","text":"FrameProcessor — Dual-Queue Architecture","fontSize":28,"fontFamily":2},{"id":"fp-box","type":"rectangle","x":50,"y":60,"width":1100,"height":520,"backgroundColor":"#f8f9fa","strokeColor":"#868e96","roughness":1,"opacity":20},{"id":"fp-label","type":"text","x":70,"y":70,"strokeColor":"#868e96","text":"FrameProcessor instance (each STT, LLM, TTS, etc. is one of these)","fontSize":14,"fontFamily":2},{"id":"prev-proc","type":"ellipse","x":-220,"y":180,"width":180,"height":60,"backgroundColor":"#e9ecef","strokeColor":"#495057","roughness":1,"label":{"text":"prev processor"}},{"id":"a-prev-qf","type":"arrow","x":-32,"y":209,"strokeColor":"#495057","label":{"text":"queue_frame()"},"points":[[0,0],[124,-2]],"endArrowhead":"arrow","startBinding":{"elementId":"prev-proc","focus":0,"gap":8},"endBinding":{"elementId":"input-q","focus":0,"gap":8}},{"id":"input-q","type":"rectangle","x":100,"y":140,"width":260,"height":130,"backgroundColor":"#ffc9c9","strokeColor":"#e03131","roughness":1,"label":{"text":"Input Queue\n(PriorityQueue)"}},{"id":"iq-detail","type":"text","x":100,"y":290,"strokeColor":"#c92a2a","text":"SystemFrame  → priority 1 (HIGH)\nDataFrame    → priority 2 (LOW)\nControlFrame → priority 2 (LOW)\n\nSystemFrames always dequeued first,\neven if DataFrames arrived earlier.","fontSize":12,"fontFamily":3},{"id":"a-iq-it","type":"arrow","x":368,"y":196,"strokeColor":"#e03131","points":[[0,0],[104,-7]],"endArrowhead":"arrow","startBinding":{"elementId":"input-q","focus":0,"gap":8},"endBinding":{"elementId":"input-task","focus":0,"gap":8}},{"id":"input-task","type":"rectangle","x":480,"y":140,"width":260,"height":80,"backgroundColor":"#ffc9c9","strokeColor":"#e03131","roughness":1,"label":{"text":"Input Task\n(__input_frame_task)"}},{"id":"it-detail","type":"text","x":480,"y":240,"strokeColor":"#c92a2a","text":"while True:\n  frame = await input_queue.get()\n  if SystemFrame:\n    → process_frame() HERE (immediate)\n  else:\n    → put in Process Queue","fontSize":12,"fontFamily":3},{"id":"sys-examples","type":"text","x":770,"y":180,"strokeColor":"#862e9c","text":"Example SystemFrames processed here:\n• InterruptionFrame → _start_interruption()\n• StartFrame → boots processor\n• CancelFrame → shuts down\n• VADUserStartedSpeakingFrame\n• ErrorFrame (pushed upstream)","fontSize":12,"fontFamily":2},{"id":"a-it-pq","type":"arrow","x":610,"y":228,"strokeColor":"#1971c2","label":{"text":"non-system frames"},"points":[[0,0],[0,264]],"endArrowhead":"arrow","startBinding":{"elementId":"input-task","focus":0,"gap":8},"endBinding":{"elementId":"process-q","focus":0,"gap":8}},{"id":"process-q","type":"rectangle","x":480,"y":500,"width":260,"height":80,"backgroundColor":"#a5d8ff","strokeColor":"#1971c2","roughness":1,"label":{"text":"Process Queue\n(asyncio.Queue — FIFO)"}},{"id":"pq-detail","type":"text","x":100,"y":510,"strokeColor":"#1864ab","text":"Holds DataFrames & ControlFrames:\n• LLMTextFrame, TTSAudioRawFrame\n• TTSStartedFrame, LLMFullResponseEndFrame\n• TranscriptionFrame, etc.\n\nProcessed strictly in arrival order.","fontSize":12,"fontFamily":3},{"id":"a-pq-pt","type":"arrow","x":748,"y":540,"strokeColor":"#1971c2","points":[[0,0],[124,0]],"endArrowhead":"arrow","startBinding":{"elementId":"process-q","focus":0,"gap":8},"endBinding":{"elementId":"process-task","focus":0,"gap":8}},{"id":"process-task","type":"rectangle","x":880,"y":480,"width":240,"height":120,"backgroundColor":"#a5d8ff","strokeColor":"#1971c2","roughness":1,"label":{"text":"Process Task\n(__process_frame_task)"}},{"id":"pt-detail","type":"text","x":880,"y":620,"strokeColor":"#1864ab","text":"while True:\n  frame = await queue.get()\n  → process_frame(frame, dir)\n      ← YOUR override here\n  → you call push_frame()","fontSize":12,"fontFamily":3},{"id":"push-out","type":"ellipse","x":880,"y":740,"width":200,"height":60,"backgroundColor":"#e9ecef","strokeColor":"#495057","roughness":1,"label":{"text":"push_frame()"}},{"id":"a-pt-push","type":"arrow","x":994,"y":608,"strokeColor":"#495057","points":[[0,0],[-5,124]],"endArrowhead":"arrow","startBinding":{"elementId":"process-task","focus":0,"gap":8},"endBinding":{"elementId":"push-out","focus":0,"gap":8}},{"id":"push-detail","type":"text","x":880,"y":820,"strokeColor":"#495057","text":"DOWNSTREAM → next.queue_frame(frame)\nUPSTREAM   → prev.queue_frame(frame)\nErrors     → always UPSTREAM via push_error()","fontSize":12,"fontFamily":3},{"id":"next-proc","type":"ellipse","x":880,"y":900,"width":180,"height":60,"backgroundColor":"#e9ecef","strokeColor":"#495057","roughness":1,"label":{"text":"next processor"}},{"id":"a-push-next","type":"arrow","x":974,"y":808,"strokeColor":"#495057","points":[[0,0],[2,84]],"endArrowhead":"arrow","startBinding":{"elementId":"push-out","focus":0,"gap":8},"endBinding":{"elementId":"next-proc","focus":0,"gap":8}},{"id":"int-zone","type":"rectangle","x":50,"y":1020,"width":1100,"height":230,"backgroundColor":"#fff3bf","strokeColor":"#f08c00","strokeStyle":"dashed","roughness":1,"opacity":25},{"id":"int-title","type":"text","x":80,"y":1040,"strokeColor":"#e8590c","text":"INTERRUPTION SCENARIO:  User speaks while bot is talking","fontSize":18,"fontFamily":2},{"id":"int-steps","type":"text","x":80,"y":1080,"strokeColor":"#495057","text":"1. InterruptionFrame arrives in Input Queue as SystemFrame (HIGH priority — jumps ahead of pending audio)\n\n2. Input Task dequeues it immediately — calls _start_interruption()\n\n3. _start_interruption() CANCELS the Process Task (stops whatever it was doing mid-frame)\n\n4. Process Queue is DRAINED:\n     • TTSAudioRawFrame chunks  →  DROPPED  (10 pending audio chunks gone)\n     • LLMTextFrame tokens      →  DROPPED\n     • EndFrame                 →  KEPT  (UninterruptibleFrame)\n     • FunctionCallResultFrame  →  KEPT  (UninterruptibleFrame)\n\n5. Fresh Process Task created → pipeline is clean and ready for the new user turn","fontSize":13,"fontFamily":2},{"id":"dm-zone","type":"rectangle","x":50,"y":1300,"width":1100,"height":80,"backgroundColor":"#d0bfff","strokeColor":"#7048e8","strokeStyle":"dashed","roughness":1,"opacity":30},{"id":"dm-text","type":"text","x":80,"y":1315,"strokeColor":"#7048e8","text":"DIRECT MODE  (enable_direct_mode=True)\n\nSkips BOTH queues — queue_frame() calls process_frame() synchronously.\nUsed by PipelineSource / PipelineSink for zero-overhead at pipeline boundaries.","fontSize":13,"fontFamily":2},{"id":"legend","type":"text","x":50,"y":1420,"strokeColor":"#868e96","text":"Color key:   RED = system / priority path       BLUE = regular data path       YELLOW = interruption       PURPLE = direct mode","fontSize":13,"fontFamily":2}],"appState":{"viewBackgroundColor":"#ffffff","gridSize":null}}